{"tid":463054,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"遊泰國注意！12月起 當地買SIM卡須面部掃描","createTime":"2017-11-09T06:45:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T07:33:50.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cc1525ff3b77e0daa8dce36b98a048f938c7da54","tid":463054,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:45:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.gotrip.hk/travel-news/%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B-sim%E5%8D%A1-%E9%9D%A2%E9%83%A8%E6%8E%83%E6%8F%8F-%E8%83%A1%E6%85%A7%E5%86%B2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gotrip.hk%2Ftravel-news%2F%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E5%259C%258B-sim%25E5%258D%25A1-%25E9%259D%25A2%25E9%2583%25A8%25E6%258E%2583%25E6%258F%258F-%25E8%2583%25A1%25E6%2585%25A7%25E5%2586%25B2%2F&d=e%2B11qaBe0KYJzSebqjOx1f%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=0d8703af\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gotrip.hk/travel-news/%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B-sim%E5%8D%A1-%E9%9D%A2%E9%83%A8%E6%8E%83%E6%8F%8F-%E8%83%A1%E6%85%A7%E5%86%B2/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n12月起出卡 須登記指紋或面部描掃<br />\n<br />\n為打擊網上編案，泰國傳播及電信委員會在周一宣布，12月15日開始，全國推動生物辨識SIM卡計劃，所有用戶若要購買新SIM卡，除了實名登記之外，必須登記指紋或面部掃描，以打擊近年利用預付SIM卡發動的恐襲或網上詐騙。"},{"pid":"30ec4da797e288584bb4051e06b25182c4f9958b","tid":463054,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:46:09.000Z","msg":"由於此措施包括遊客，以後一落機在機場出卡，除了實名用護照登記，也要提供指紋或面容資料影張相，估計等候開卡時間會增長。泰國通胡慧冲指，現時不少港人會在鴨寮街或香港的電訊店預購SIM卡，這些已經流通市面的SIM卡或許在12月15日後用唔到，建議抵達泰國時在當地開卡購買。<br />\n<br />\nSIM卡貨量或短暫不足<br />\n<br />\n另外Roger指出，昨日消息一出，立即有網友詢問他，說昨日在曼谷多間商場內的True、AIS電訊商買SIM卡都買不到，懷疑與新措施有關。不過Roger大派定心丸，因為SIM卡此等日常通訊用品絕不會禁止購買，可能只是新例下暫有不夠貨情況，而且面容資料即是影張相存檔，入境時候也要，故此不用為此而驚恐。"},{"pid":"69a01e0d17aa85a6cb5ed30e113a6ffaa7316a28","tid":463054,"uid":74497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:47:10.000Z","msg":"降<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a8bcdf087fa0a7802d713ca22cf3cd9bc7deb5a","tid":463054,"uid":39576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:48:46.000Z","msg":"十二月去先搞D咁既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"609729c8845e01367f0fbd5e444abd9f7894456f","tid":463054,"uid":17919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:54:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e0414a8499f21568df7d61a2d2d03cb889bf04","tid":463054,"uid":17919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:55:57.000Z","msg":"慣左一降落就book車，咁咪gg"},{"pid":"0769fabdb959648f53d5e6b6ccc03f95ba4e870b","tid":463054,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T07:16:20.000Z","msg":"之前開通左的卡,去到沖值可能  work"},{"pid":"e4556630f34e3bd2343f5820f1e7484cf1f30448","tid":463054,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T07:33:50.000Z","msg":"有無政治撚講下<br />\n同新泰王集權有無關係"}]}